('digital-ai', 2, 'problem_block', 'Why Digital Efforts Fail', 'Common pitfalls in digital transformation and tooling.', 'light', '{"list": ["Tools are purchased without value definition", "Data lives in silos (CRM, CS platform, NPS, tickets)", "Customer insights aren’t turned into actions", "AI is superficial, not embedded in journeys", "CX & CS tooling has no ROI measurement"]}', NULL, 'Problem statement block'),
